    "description": "<p>TAI ER was launched in 2015 Guangzhou, is a unique chain restaurant that featuring Suancai &amp; Fish and aims to introduce classic Sichuan Cuisine to the world.&nbsp;Listed on the Hong Kong Stock Exchange as an international holding company (HK.09922).</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Currently has 400+ branches in most of the cities in China, such as Beijing, Shanghai, Guangzhou and Shenzhen.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>First oversea branch is located in Singapore. TAI ER are spreading their wings to more new market at Singapore, Malaysia, Canada，Thailand, Korea and United States, hoping the world enjoys this unique and flavorful Sichuan taste</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Expanding fast worldwide!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>【太二酸菜鱼】是九毛九集团旗下餐饮品牌。九毛九集团经营至今已逾25年，就职员工逾1万人，并在2020年1月于香港交易所挂牌上市成为国际控股公司（HK.09922）。</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>【太二酸菜鱼】于2015年在中国广州成立，是一家传承中国川菜美味、主打川菜经典菜品酸 菜鱼的创新互联网餐饮品牌。门店辐射中国大部分城市，主要集中在北京、上海、 广州、深圳等一线城市。并于2019年拓展海外市场，首店选址新加坡，自开业以 来，深受新加坡食客喜爱。未来将布局加拿大、新马泰、韩国、美国等地区，为 世界带来川菜的酸爽滋味。</p>\n<p><br></p>",
